# ============================================================
# Vercel KV (Required for trace persistence in production)
# ============================================================
# Without Vercel KV, traces are stored in memory and lost between
# serverless function invocations.
#
# To set up Vercel KV:
# 1. Go to your Vercel project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Storage tab
# 3. Click "Create Database" â†’ Select "KV"
# 4. Click "Create" and follow the prompts
# 5. The environment variables will be automatically added
#
# Or manually set these variables:
# KV_REST_API_URL=https://your-kv-instance.kv.vercel-storage.com
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=your-token-here
#
# Alternative: Use Upstash Redis (free tier available)
# Create a database at https://upstash.com/ and use the REST API credentials
